# Deploy ONLY the chart calculator + its Python API to Vercel.
# The library site stays on GitHub Pages (README: "GitHub Pages serves it as-is");
# keeping the library OUT of the Vercel build means it is never duplicated there —
# Vercel serves just viewer/astrology-viewer.html and api/calculate-chart.
#
# Kept for the Vercel build:  api/  requirements.txt  viewer/  vercel.json
# Everything below is library/tooling and is excluded from Vercel:

grammars/
research/
scripts/
plan/
docs/
*.md
index.html
channels.html
wheel.html
theme.css
voices.json
_collection.json
ids.json
recursive-eco.json
check.py
